Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:26.48,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:32.16,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:37.01,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.82,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.63,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.99,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.76,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:55.19,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:03:01.44,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:06.25,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:10.74,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:58.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:05.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:26.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:32.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:37.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:55.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:03:01.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:06.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:10.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.47,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H968E8B&\pos(408,714)}電視\N空調 \N電風扇\N音響\N遊戲機\N同上\N{\fs55}數碼相機\N電動車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.47,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1520,736)}打印機 \N冰箱\N 微波爐\N 吸塵器\N 縫紉機 \N洗衣機 \N取暖器\N 電飯鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:32.85,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)}第五話 三個臭皮匠賽過諸葛亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我從泰叔那裡打聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:33.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說有個叫吉田的流浪漢在回收舊家電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一台電視可是能賣3000元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊雛 咱們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,該去哪裡找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是沒什麼人來的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前還看到過類似呢 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間就找到電視了 而且還有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 真是一座寶山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你先在這裡守一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了 加把勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真是重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到一天的工夫 你就找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個流浪漢居然過得這麼有品位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「居然」？ 你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的寶山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這些是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你能找這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 這不是電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在顯像管這東西不值錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過因為能賣給東南亞 所以我就收了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你給多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:50.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,10元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有數字信號的液晶電視才能買三千元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找這種電視可不太容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個流浪的搞回收幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他點燃了我的鬥志…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣的話 我偏要找一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到啊 兩個人的話這已經是極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我找人來幫我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也把瞳給叫來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的朋友 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我根本聯繫不到她啊 就算她是我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會… 你和雛認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我學校裡的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你跟雛早就是朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 天馬上就要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天估計找不到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但好不容易才找到你們兩個來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:18.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去那邊找 咱們再加把勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 媽 咱們之前不是買了台新電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前還想把舊的給扔了來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽其實不用特地把它裝箱子裡的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就放這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這樣杏子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還要找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在連一台都沒找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在瞳肯定也在努力找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:09.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 可不能亂大件垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直不說話 是說不出口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是說了真話 他似乎也不會相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:21.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他信了 問題依然不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先跟你的家人聯繫一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 千萬不要… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是想責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我從開始就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你實話跟我說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被家長逼著出來扔東西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們得學學瞳 分頭去找電視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想買電視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客廳不是有一台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再另買一台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些應該夠買一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 就這麼輕易答應真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 好不容易喝得挺開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就別在這兒開家庭會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都要買 那就在「驚嚇相機」那裡買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,積分卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把電視給帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不… 這怎麼看都是全新的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要賣這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在試探我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 完全不知道她在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,車費一共是5920元 你會付錢給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我幫她付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就當是我收這台電視的錢可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能付的話倒是也行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這台電視是她剛剛在「驚嚇相機」買的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這事別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒找到電視
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在半路上沒能扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你好像不太高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是瞳啊 區區一台電視不用太高興對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又裝在箱子裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:47.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這話也不該我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們乾脆賣到回收店去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到今天賺到了這麼多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是瞳找到的 我收下真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是找到了 要是沒聽你說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會拿它來換錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱們三個人平分了吧 這樣好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼突然間就想要錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說遊戲很有趣 我想跟你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經全說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,買到電視了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 可能過個幾天就會送來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把電視給賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那賣的錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我想問的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我付車錢用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣 猜謎遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 健吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點回去的話老媽會發火的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸那不是三島嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 Little Song酒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是松谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 他進去那裡了誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老師跟學生在酒吧裡見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是不純異性交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會揉胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,會揉啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接下來的妄想進行不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知識 如果再有多一點知識的話！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 那個該死蘿莉控老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必須制裁他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8}懷疑松谷進行不純異性交往對策本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,諸位 對為了解決事件而聚集起來的你們表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們不想讓太多人知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為還關係到她的名譽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳才不會做那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是你們看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧您說的 相澤警視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在說上頭的人是看不見現場發生的事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要玩警察遊戲的話就把雛也喊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那傢伙來了也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然完全沒用處 但是吉祥物還是能當的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是別那麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法 健吾巡查部長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去把雛巡查喊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 貴志警部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：警視，警部，巡查部長，巡查都是警察官的職位，階級依次遞減
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩人只是在玩而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警部 我把雛巡查帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:34.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你不報任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她過來就這個語氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能請你先交給我來辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警視親自來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了澄清她的嫌疑才進行的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢噢 相澤警視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是幹勁十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這是在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖這麼說 姑且先刺探一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來啊瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在晚上的繁華街那邊看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,補習班 我是去補習班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一帶的話是開心塾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有個叫吉田的講師很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你是在跟他學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 吉田老師沒教我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很受歡迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊記錯了是吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不對 是吉野老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還說「哎呀」 你是中國人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話反而想讓她說一下「阿魯」之類詞尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：這裡捏他神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不冷靜一下相澤紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別丟了原本目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過並沒有那個講師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說不出口是紗夜你搞錯了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是頭疼 哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 雖然我是不信啦但這個態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛應該是被捲進什麼麻煩事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來啊瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道Little Song嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好髒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島把牛奶噴出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧了啊 我都黏乎乎的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果是三島的牛奶的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:33.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得變得好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我說的是瞳你喜歡的「中央公園」的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出了這樣的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全是我瞎編的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 她沒說漏嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你有真的有打算讓犯人落網嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是在跟三島玩而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相澤警視
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慌慌張張的瞳 總而言之就是很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你這不就是在玩而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}散夥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我們自己來搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 還真敢說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這個時候要分開走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,樓梯只有這個 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來怎麼辦 警部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩個去收集證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們有貓膩 可能在學校裡也會獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在 在學校 太糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣啊 感覺都緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三島 能稍微到準備室來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,準備室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡面他們孤男寡女的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孤男寡女地做什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:06.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想像到這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 進去捉個現成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就算真的看到了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了搜查也是不得已的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:15.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 講義掉到四處都是了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 給三島搭把手搬回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說三島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在做什麼不能告訴別人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什 你指什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是多麼顯而易見的可疑態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說是蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那雖然是不能對人說 不過有人會感到高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,樂意？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 當然我不知道你說的是什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,講義…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要逮住你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,逮住你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要把你抓個現成！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別說是拿過去了 這都散成一地回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢 知道了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相澤 你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 絕對要解決事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必須對那個該死的邪門歪道的老師降下正義鐵錘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩人情緒好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 是三島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:48.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\fn@思源黑体 CN Regular\frz269.8\c&H81B196&\3c&HD4FFE5&\b1\pos(632,488)}大人的玩具 幹個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 接下來就等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 現在在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不不難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這不只是松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所謂的「援交」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 瞳才不會那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到犯罪現場後就慌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是說了「有人會感到高興」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是新田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田是雛你老爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛的老爸進去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是說雛的老爸在跟三島交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊雛 那邊有你的新媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也暈頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊是酒吧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也有從那裡展開的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會容許它展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那種事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就完全出局了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:47.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 瞳 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:52.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相澤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個情況 是安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然搞不清楚情況  但這不是援交
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 不是最糟的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我們在擔心你哦三島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在做調酒師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,酒吧可不是小孩子能來的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是打算裝作不認識我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被我們看到這副模樣後她還以為還能矇混過關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 沒你這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警視 犯人在否認罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 給我坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子老家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請別在 店裡進行審判…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:57.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:03.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們幾個 是擔心你有個萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果瞳你不想說的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 至少告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們 是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起紗夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼知道我叫紗夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別再讓老家的媽媽再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞞著大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:55.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那老實地招供吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:59.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說「我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:05.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:07.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,複述
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音再大一點!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再大聲一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再融入些心意 用偶像自我介紹風格說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:29.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是個中學生 卻在做著調酒師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這是在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你們 為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟三島搞混了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳真的跟三島很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:02.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了個高級的笨蛋啊
